Meta-data query interface.

          Description

Interface Summary
IEntityQueryVisitor Entity querying interface NOT to implemented by clients directly.
IEntityVisitor Visitor interface for Entities NOT to implemented by clients directly.
IMetaDataModelContext Provisional API - subject to change
IMetaDataVisitor Common interface for Entity and Trait visitors NOT to implemented by clients directly.
IResultSet Results from a metadata query.
ITaglibDomainMetaDataModelContext Context for determining the Model to locate in the MetaDataManager Should NOT be implemented by clients Provisional API - subject to change
ITraitQueryVisitor Trait querying interface NOT to implemented by clients directly.
ITraitVisitor Visitor interface for Traits NOT to implemented by clients directly.
 

Class Summary
AbstractEntityQueryVisitor Abstract class implmenting IEntityQueryVisitor that concrete subclasses should provide implementations Provisional API - subject to change
AbstractEntityVisitor Abstract implementation that concrete subclasses should ovveride Provisional API - subject to change
AbstractMetaDataVisitor Abstract class implementing IMetaDataVisitor Provisional API - subject to change
AbstractResultSet Abstract implementation of IResultSet that developers may subclass.
AbstractTraitQueryVisitor Abstract implmentation of ITraitQueryVisitor that subclasses should use to provide implmentation Provisional API - subject to change
AbstractTraitVisitor Abstract Trait visitor Provisional API - subject to change
EmptyResultSet Implementation of an empty result set Provisional API - subject to change
TaglibDomainMetaDataQueryHelper Helper class with static methods to simplify querying of a metadata model.
 

Exception Summary
MetaDataException Exception intended to be superclass of all exceptions thrown while handling metadata during query Provisional API - subject to change
